Episode 8 features member of the UofL men’s basketball team, Hercy Miller! 🏀 

It was so much fun filming with Hercy at @cherrypickingoods where the newest juice/smoothie bar in Louisville has everything basketball themed…very fitting for this interview. 

Be sure to listen to Hercy talk about his experience at the NIL Summit as well as how he prioritizes family (The Miller Gang) as a student-athlete and in the NIL space. Listen to hear all about his experience and how he balances it all!
